Fonts vendored for MathML rendering
===================================

These WOFF2 files are the Latin Modern math and text fonts shipped with the
`font/` directory of pulldown-latex 0.7.1 (github.com/carloskiki/pulldown-latex).

  latinmodern-math.woff2     Latin Modern Math
  lmroman12-regular.woff2    Latin Modern Roman 12 (regular)
  lmroman12-bold.woff2       Latin Modern Roman 12 (bold)
  lmroman12-italic.woff2     Latin Modern Roman 12 (italic)

The Latin Modern fonts are produced by GUST e-foundry and distributed under the
GUST Font License (GFL), an LPPL-based free-software licence that permits use,
redistribution, and modification.

  GUST Font License: http://www.gust.org.pl/projects/e-foundry/licenses
  Latin Modern:      http://www.gust.org.pl/projects/e-foundry/latin-modern

jumanji redistributes these fonts unmodified, embedded as base64 `data:` URIs in
the generated math stylesheet (see `src/core/math.rs`). No network fetch occurs.
